Fix things in `text` such as :
case \$pkgver in

> *.*.\*) \_kernver=\${pkgver%.\*};;
> *.*) \_kernver=\$pkgver;;

esac

This is a common pattern in APKBUILD to extract some segments from a version

Fix this in `text`:

: pkgver=2.5.16.1
  case \$pkgver in
  *.*.\*.\*) \_v=\${pkgver%.\*.\*};;
  *.*.\*) \_v=\${pkgver%.\*};;
  ) \_v=\$pkgver;;
  esac

Fix things in `text` such as :

: case \$pkgver in

  : *.*.\*) \_kernver=\${pkgver%.\*};;
    *.*) \_kernver=\$pkgver;;

  esac

and:

: case \$pkgver in
  *.*.\*) \_kernver=\${pkgver%.\*};;
  *.*) \_kernver=\$\{pkgver};;
  esac

